# Domains the workspace is allowed to reach (one per line).
# A leading dot matches the domain and all its subdomains (e.g. .github.com).
# To change the policy: edit this file and rebuild the gateway
#   (Dev Containers: Rebuild Container). The workspace cannot edit it at runtime.
# Denied requests are logged by the gateway: `docker compose logs gateway`.
# Scope: this governs RUNTIME egress only. Image build (including the claude-code
# feature's installer download) runs on the host build network and is NOT filtered
# by this allowlist.

# Anthropic / Claude Code (API, installer, docs)
.anthropic.com
.claude.ai
.claude.com

# GitHub (clone, raw content, releases; LFS objects served from S3)
.github.com
.githubusercontent.com
github-cloud.s3.amazonaws.com

# Debian packages
.debian.org

# Language package registries (match the toolchains installed via features)
.npmjs.org
pypi.org
files.pythonhosted.org
.golang.org
.nuget.org

# Node / front-end toolchain (node-gyp headers, Playwright browser binaries)
nodejs.org
cdn.playwright.dev
playwright.download.prss.microsoft.com

# Docs (browsing from the container; not required for builds)
developer.mozilla.org
typescriptlang.org
npmjs.com
